  "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
  "description": "Low-cost internet service providers have emerged to bridge the digital divide and ensure everyone has the opportunity to stay connected and participate in the modern world. See more about the details.",
  "local_image": "postImg\\2937b504-acab-4189-be94-f4d4b305f9da.webp",
  "pages": [
    {
      "page": 1,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>If you're on a tight budget, there are programs to help make internet service more affordable for low-income households. Government subsidies and low-income plans from ISPs can lower your internet bill. Let's explore these affordable plans and programs to reduce your connection costs.</p>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 2,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. Affordable Connectivity Program (ACP)</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The ACP is a program that helps low-income families afford the internet by paying part of their bill. They give $30 a month towards the bill, but if you live in a Tribal area or a place with high-cost internet, you might get $75 instead. Over 20 million households have joined the ACP by August 2023.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 3,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>2. Lifeline</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Lifeline, a program backed by the FCC, aids low-income households with discounted phone or internet services. Recipients can receive a minimum $9.25 reduction on landline, wireless, broadband, or bundled services. Those residing on Tribal lands may qualify for an extra $25 discount. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 4,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>3. Emergency Broadband Benefit (EBB)</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Starting on May 12, 2021, you could sign up for the Emergency Broadband Benefit program. It gives qualified households a discount of up to $50–$75 each month. If you need a new laptop, desktop, or tablet, you could get up to $100 off one of those too. Only one monthly service and one new device are allowed per household.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 5,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>4. Connect Home USA</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>ConnectHomeUSA started in 2015 to bridge the digital gap for families in HUD-assisted housing. It now operates in 80+ US communities, with new ones added annually. Residents can access helpful resources for affordable internet and devices. Others can start their own inclusion program, even if not in these areas.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 6,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>5. Internet First</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Internet First is a program that provides cheap internet service for those who live in RCN, Grande, or Wave service areas and those who qualify for any of these public service programs:</p>\n<p> – Medicaid</p>\n<p> – Public housing assistance</p>\n<p> – Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP)</p>\n<p> – Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF)</p>\n<p> – Supplemental Security Income (SSI)</p>\n<p> – Head Start National School Lunch Program (NSLP) or Head Start</p>\n<p> – Low Income Home Energy Assistance Program (LIHEAP)</p>\n<p> – Women, Infants, and Children program (WIC)</p>\n<p> – Federal Pell Grant (applicable only for Illinois and Colorado)</p>\n<p> – VA Pension</p>\n<p> – Tribal assistance</p>\n<p>You can get internet speeds up to 25Mbps for $9.95 per month through this program.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 7,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>6. Spectrum</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_7\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_7.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_7.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_7.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_7.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Spectrum has an Internet Assist program like Xfinity's Internet Essentials. For $14.99/month, you get up to 30 Mbps speed (WiFi may vary), no data limit, and no contract. It's for households with a member who receives National School Lunch Program, Community Eligibility Provision of NSLP, or Supplemental Security Income (age 65 or older).</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 8,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>7. AT&amp;T</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_8\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_8.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_8.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_8.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_8.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>AT&amp;T’s Access program offers internet speeds up to 10Mbps to eligible low-income families for $5–$10 per month. To qualify for Access, customers must have at least one family member who participates in the SNAP program.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 9,
      "title": "How To Get Free Internet Service",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How To Get Free Internet Service</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>8. Optimum</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Free Internet Service_9\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_9.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_9.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_9.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-to-get-free-internet-service/how-to-get-free-internet-service_9.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>If you have Optimum, you can get Altice Advantage Internet for just $14.99 per month. It's super fast, with speeds up to 30Mbps. And it's not just for anyone - you gotta have a child on NSLP, be a US military vet on public assistance or receive SSI (if you're 65+).</p>\n</img></div>"
    }
  ]
